{"tid":6204,"cid":21,"subCid":0,"title":"[起步太遲］有無巴打願意由零開始教小弟鋼琴","createTime":"2016-11-27T08:41:07.000Z","updateTime":"2016-11-28T11:05:48.000Z","uid":397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"04eeb5885011cf3e80e32a1f2d7c5a580db6e1b2","tid":6204,"uid":397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T08:41:07.000Z","msg":"小弟今年18 由細到大一直都想學琴但無耐以前屋企真係無多餘錢可以比我去學<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有無有心既巴打願意由零開始去教我？價錢可議<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我唔求咩考到8級樂理 我只求彈到就得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n因為小弟係連譜都唔識睇 所以我知教我應該幾煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但如果有人可以教我我真係會努力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77eb5cfa70416ed56d47a457e0dac3d760c79e54","tid":6204,"uid":397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T08:45:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"789f2212282c1364b0deac9e23cd6732ac26796d","tid":6204,"uid":397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T08:54:03.000Z","msg":"推爆佢啦"},{"pid":"c91cb849440140b3a96e3a3a84d51f7a1114aed2","tid":6204,"uid":5920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T09:17:22.000Z","msg":"有冇telegram"},{"pid":"189fae11286ce9438ceed3da769a5dcf393edeeb","tid":6204,"uid":397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T11:04:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有冇telegram</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有"},{"pid":"8d81e838f4f02f382c395a50ed9b60f5c17cc411","tid":6204,"uid":397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T11:05:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>有冇telegram</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nedwinkw"}]}